## âš–ï¸ Comparing the Philosophies

| Aspect                          | **Brazil**                               | **Estonia**                                   |
| ------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| **When tax is paid**            | When profit is earned                    | When profit is distributed                    |
| **Dividend taxation**           | 0 % (already taxed at corporate level)   | 20â€“22 % (only at distribution)                |
